item.title: Projects
item.description: Clara Link to heading Clara is an extensible AI assistant that seamlessly interacts with various plugins to fulfill complex tasks, all through natural language conversations powered by OpenAI. Reef-Mon Link to heading Reef-Mon is a simple tool to monitor the status of a Reef using Go, InfluxDB, and a Raspberry PI. Serverless File Upload Link to heading Serverless File Upload is a File upload system with burn after read capabilities built on top of AWS using the chalice framework.
